      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that gets the job done? This car is a fantastic choice for anyone needing reliable transportation on a budget! It shows some honest wear from its years on the road, but it still runs strong and offers a comfortable ride for your daily commute. It's the perfect opportunity to own a solid, functional vehicle at a great price!",
