    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that doesn't need to be perfect. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dings on the passenger side, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to keep it in top shape.",
